{"tid":2188662,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"日本民調：最多受訪者認為菅義偉是下任首相理想人選","createTime":"2020-09-04T11:17:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-04T11:17:33.000Z","uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"13c773fe3213e7325fd0bd7ea64d8d2a1ba7efdc","tid":2188662,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T11:17:33.000Z","msg":"日本最新民意調查顯示，最多受訪者認為，內閣官房長官菅義偉是下任首相理想人選。<br />\n<br />\n據日本《朝日新聞》周五發布的民意調查結果，菅義偉獲38%受訪者支持成為下任首相。早前在多項民調都領先的前防衛大臣石破茂，現時就以25%支持率排第二；至於前外相岸田文雄支持率就只得5%。<br />\n<br />\n日本執政自民黨將於本月14日舉行黨總裁選舉，當選者將接替因健康理由辭職的安倍晉三出任首相。<span class=\"red\">《朝日新聞》另一項民調顯示，71%的受訪者對持續執政七年多的安倍政權給予好評。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=404319\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D404319&d=HMiOmB7b1AqxO%2BCwCPl1cUyCzF7GSvQxQofikz39bzk%3D&h=f79d647d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D404319&h=a5b5c0cb\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=404319</a><br />\n<br />\n石破茂必勝，日中友好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}